<h3 class="wp-block-heading" style="padding-bottom:0;font-size:30px">What is Full Site Editing in WordPress?</h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"18px"}}} -->
<p style="font-size:18px">Full Site Editing in WordPress refers to a feature that allows users to create and edit their website's entire layout, including the header, footer, and other structural elements, using a visual editor.</p>
