<h3 class="wp-block-heading" style="padding-bottom:0;font-size:30px">What are the benefits of Full Site Editing in WordPress?</h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"18px"}}} -->
<p style="font-size:18px">Full Site Editing in WordPress allows users to create and edit their website more efficiently and with more control. It enables users to create unique and custom designs without needing to have advanced coding skills.</p>
