<h3 class="wp-block-heading" style="padding-bottom:0;font-size:30px">What are some popular WordPress themes that support Full Site Editing?</h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"18px"}}} -->
<p style="font-size:18px">Some popular WordPress themes that support Full Site Editing include the Kadence Theme, the Qubely Theme, and the GenerateBlocks Theme. These themes have built-in support for Full Site Editing, allowing users to create custom designs without needing to know how to code.</p>
